news.title: Adani family invests another Rs 6,661 crore in Ambuja Cement
news.para: Adani family invests Rs 6,661 crore in Ambuja Cement, increasing stake to 66.7%. The fund infusion will be instrumental in increasing the capacity to 140 million tonnes per annum by 2028.

news.title: S&P cuts Sweden's SBB rating to selective default
news.para: The property group, which has been scrambling to cut its debt mountain, recently repaid some bondholders a fraction of what they were owed in a tender offer.

news.title: UltraTech Cement to acquire 26% equity in O2 Renewable Energy
news.para: The cement maker company has entered into an energy supply agreement and share subscription and shareholders agreement with O2 Renewable Energy.
